{"tid":1728302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"識得個南斯拉夫內戰生還者，幫你問佢答","createTime":"2019-11-16T21:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T10:50:47.000Z","uid":164430,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d77007cc5c8d0031e3332823b758b49677c83e7","tid":1728302,"uid":164430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T21:06:48.000Z","msg":"[南斯拉夫內戰餘生錄]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Warfare/M.1340814455.A.6DE.html?fbclid=IwAR1p--XTg8P4cgRvm0vB74drNLtEZ8g8xgyhBDyaI-c2zeOMI0PQVEwMtho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FWarfare%2FM.1340814455.A.6DE.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1p--XTg8P4cgRvm0vB74drNLtEZ8g8xgyhBDyaI-c2zeOMI0PQVEwMtho&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=66fd6ac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Warfare/M.1340814455.A.6DE.html?fbclid=IwAR1p--XTg8P4cgRvm0vB74drNLtEZ8g8xgyhBDyaI-c2zeOMI0PQVEwMtho</a><br />\n<br />\n頭先係ptt見到呢篇口述歷史<br />\n<br />\n先醒起我有個friend，佢就係薩拉熱窩圍城戰嘅生還者之一，當時圍城圍左成1,425日，基本上生存到落黎嘅都一大堆經歷。<br />\n<br />\n覺得香港宜家已經係內戰狀態...可能知多D親身經驗對大家有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們隨便問，我再轉述俾佢聽。"},{"pid":"dd025645772c39ef303610f3a9b2fe82297adecf","tid":1728302,"uid":100920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T21:08:46.000Z","msg":"this war of mine"},{"pid":"509f9593d69029fbe0fa1816d7c79db4cdaa132d","tid":1728302,"uid":164430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd025645772c39ef303610f3a9b2fe82297adecf","tid":1728302,"uid":100920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T21:08:46.000Z","msg":"this war of mine"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T21:39:33.000Z","msg":"睇過我呀哥玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似好難玩咁"},{"pid":"5af4b3ade7df4f68ae520a8df55ba901479e7f07","tid":1728302,"uid":114328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:02:08.000Z","msg":"好睇你點代入隻game <br />\n唔好怕難 試下玩 <br />\n無記錯廠商唔介意你down 玩老翻 玩完鐘意再比錢 都得"},{"pid":"95fc8b9ef27f7e4acde239cf7564285764a54013","tid":1728302,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:04:22.000Z","msg":"Tunnel of Hope<br />\nThe UN soldiers are smurf only<br />\n有無去War Children Museum?<br />\n 我之前睇過本書叫 Logavina Street<br />\n 其實我反而 想知道當地人點樣睇呢一個國家嘅未來"},{"pid":"3bb2750e16a491b017eb7e4d92a8d23ca77deec6","tid":1728302,"uid":164430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95fc8b9ef27f7e4acde239cf7564285764a54013","tid":1728302,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:04:22.000Z","msg":"Tunnel of Hope<br />\nThe UN soldiers are smurf only<br />\n有無去War Children Museum?<br />\n 我之前睇過本書叫 Logavina Street<br />\n 其實我反而 想知道當地人點樣睇呢一個國家嘅未來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:43:24.000Z","msg":"有去呀<br />\n<br />\nWar Childhood Museum就係Logavina Street架喎，本書講d咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢宜家訓左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我聽日問佢<br />\n但佢唔止一次同我講呢個國家係無希望<br />\n三個政府各自為政，又同泛民一樣玩左幾十年都係同一批人撈政治飯食<br />\n佢又成日講打完仗後淨返低嘅都係自私嘅人，教出黎嘅細路又只會係咁，同時加埋戰後好多農村人走黎城市搵食（佢住薩拉熱窩）人民質素好低，d年青人都係掛住食玩訓不時進取<br />\n基本上就係無未來<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢覺得巴爾幹半島太多留低嘅問題未解決，遲早會再打仗"},{"pid":"4d9bec4064e60ef5893dd6f8835bf951ff58d385","tid":1728302,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:44:56.000Z","msg":"我住過Sarajevo間War Hostel<br />\n同個host傾咗好耐<br />\n佢個故事真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dd027dff46b9f2a33044c5ac3e404d766c76a6","tid":1728302,"uid":164430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d9bec4064e60ef5893dd6f8835bf951ff58d385","tid":1728302,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:44:56.000Z","msg":"我住過Sarajevo間War Hostel<br />\n同個host傾咗好耐<br />\n佢個故事真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:51:37.000Z","msg":"願閒其詳<br />\n<br />\n乜有間war hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" cla